    "body": "Another note -- right now, for event decoding to work, you need to know the *deployed* context hash of the contract emitting the event.  For the debugger purposes, it should also work with the *constructor* context hash!\r\n\r\nAlso, for use in the debugger, we probably want an option `extras: \"strictest\"` or something where it doesn't consider the possibility of library events at all (even though in the decoder those aren't considered \"extras\").",
